ona_get_data.Rd

Retrieve specific dataset by form ID from specific user

ona_get_data(base_url = "https://api.ona.io", auth_mode = "token", form_id)

Arguments

base_url

ONA URL. Default is https://api.ona.io.
auth_mode

Password or token? Default is token.
form_id

Form identifier.

Value

A tibble of retrieved dataset.

Examples

ona_get_data(form_id = 276175)
